name: 40 Pack - FR156-2RS (3/16 x 5/16 x 1/8 inch) Flanged Ball Bearing
description:
RC Car & Truck Econo Power bearing Flanged 10 packs are the most affordable way to replace stock bearings with high quality standard bearings. Boca's Econo Power RC Bearings have long been the industry standard for backyard bashers the world over. These bearings have a flange, chrome steel races, balls, retainers and heavy duty rubber seals. All Econo Power bearings are packed in grease and will require a short break in period to loosen up. Each kit contains 10 bearings and is available for a limited time only at just 99 cents per bearing!
